OL,3,CLabour promises to implement
OL,4,CHillsborough Law if elected
OL,6,FCampaigners have been calling for new
OL,7,Flegislation to prevent the experiences
OL,8,Fof families of the 97 Liverpool fans
OL,9,Fwho were killed in the 1989
OL,10,FHillsborough disaster happening again,
OL,11,Fand to help victims of other scandals
OL,12,Fto get justice.
OL,14,FIn its manifesto, published on
OL,15,FThursday 13 June, the party said:
OL,16,F"Labour will introduce a 'Hillsborough
OL,17,FLaw' which will place a legal duty of
OL,18,Fcandour on public servants and
OL,19,Fauthorities, and provide legal aid for
OL,20,Fvictims of disasters or state-related
OL,21,Fdeaths."
