OL,6,FIn December the government stopped
OL,7,Fshort on implementing Hillsborough Law
OL,8,Fin its long-awaited response to a
OL,9,Freport into the experiences of the
OL,10,Fbereaved families.
OL,12,FInstead it signed up to a Hillsborough
OL,13,FCharter, pledging to place the public
OL,14,Finterest above its own reputation,
OL,15,Fclaiming a "Hillsborough Law"
OL,16,Fincorporating a legal duty of candour
OL,17,Fwas not necessary.
