OL,3,CLabour promises to implement
OL,4,CHillsborough Law if elected
OL,6,FNinety-seven men, women and children
OL,7,Fdied as a result of a crush on the
OL,8,Fterraces at the FA Cup semi-final
OL,9,Fbetween Liverpool and Nottingham
OL,10,FForest in Sheffield on April 15 1989.
OL,12,FIt is hoped a Hillsborough Law could
OL,13,Fhelp bereaved families and survivors
OL,14,Fin other disaster situations involving
OL,15,Fpublic bodies, such as the Grenfell
OL,16,FTower inquiry, and the inquiries into
OL,17,Fthe Manchester Arena attack and the
OL,18,FGovernment's handling of the
OL,19,Fcoronavirus outbreak.
OL,21,FWhat is the Hillsborough Law?
