OL,3,CLabour promises to implement
OL,4,CHillsborough Law if elected
OL,6,FThe law came from a review of the
OL,7,Fexperiences of the Hillsborough
OL,8,Ffamilies by former Bishop of Liverpool
OL,9,Fthe Right Reverend James Jones - 'The
OL,10,FPatronising Disposition of
OL,11,FUnaccountable Power'.
OL,13,FIt was published in 2017 and detailed
OL,14,F25 recommendations to reform the
OL,15,Fsystem. It is those recommendations,
OL,16,Fand what campaigners say are failures
OL,17,Fof criminal trials related to
OL,18,FHillsborough, which form the basis of
OL,19,Fthe Hillsborough Law.
